區，<br />\n亦向海外華人證明，向全世界證明，<br />\n呢個就係一國兩制嘅下場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時，亦有可能係上頭以林鄭下台，<br />\n張建宗作過渡，<br />\n消吓大家嘅氣<br />\n然後，<strong><ins>就沒有然後</ins></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c9b6e19a76caa4b523fea3e42844df4306484ebc","tid":1368113,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91666b56f61c463a014859cd9c654168b3dce63e","tid":1368113,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府文人高層都被下層武官批鬥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 武官就不斷（／被有心人士）推高水溫<br />\n<br />\n學另外巴打話齋，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">張建宗文官高層被下層武官插，都係<strong><ins>劇本之一</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">劇本<br />\n黑警 威脅 政府<br />\n政府 call 老解<br />\n老解 vs 黑警+白衣人<br />\n一國一制正式落實</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔通吹風吹到咁行就係出呢招？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂攞正牌入嚟香港平亂<br />\n大家醒水，睇嚟有勢力仲想翻盤 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M3cUamt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM3cUamt.jpg&h=f478ebda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一出，更加唔使旨意奪取中華民國台澎金馬地區，<br />\n亦向海外華人證明，向全世界證明，<br />\n呢個就係一國兩制嘅下場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同時，亦有可能係上頭以林鄭下台，<br />\n張建宗作過渡，<br />\n消吓大家嘅氣<br />\n然後，<strong><ins>就沒有然後</ins></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"總之張建宗都係仆街陷家剷"},{"pid":"a2172177478970766864a33e